<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Your business insurance policy has now expired</b>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I’m sorry to see that you decided not to stay with Kingsbridge for another year.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>However,&nbsp;<b>it’s&nbsp;<u>not</u>&nbsp;too late to avoid a gap in cover</b>. If you have changed your mind or did not mean to let your policy lapse, I can&nbsp;<b>restart your policy within 30 days of your expiry date</b>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively, you can always give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you don’t renew within this 30-day window and still wish to be covered by Kingsbridge, I’ll have to requote your insurance policy which may take more time and may result in a gap in your insurance coverage.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>